This sample demonstrates the PictureTaker in a basic Cocoa application. It uses IB to create a window and handles all the basic events needed for a normal Cocoa application. 

Version 1.0

- This sample should present a reasonably complete correctly formed Cocoa application which can be used as a starting point for using the PictureTaker in a Cocoa applications. 

Comments and bugs are welcome at: <http://developer.apple.com/bugreporter>

